00:08:21.125 --> 00:08:24.041
Paramachaitanyan,

00:08:24.250 --> 00:08:28.333
Adi Shaktin voiman armosta.

00:08:29.208 --> 00:08:32.208
Mutta silti

00:08:33.709 --> 00:08:38.667
